		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:heading {"level":1} -->
<h1>About AquaLuxe</h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Welcome to AquaLuxe, where passion for aquatic life meets exceptional service and expertise. Since our founding in 2010, we've been dedicated to providing premium aquarium products, expert advice, and professional services to aquarium enthusiasts of all levels.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Our mission is to help our customers create and maintain beautiful, healthy aquatic environments while promoting responsible and sustainable aquarium keeping practices.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Our Story</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>AquaLuxe began as a small local fish store founded by marine biologist Dr. James Anderson. With a PhD in Marine Biology and a lifelong passion for aquatic ecosystems, Dr. Anderson set out to create a different kind of aquarium store—one that combined scientific expertise with exceptional customer service.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Over the years, AquaLuxe has grown from a small local shop to a comprehensive aquarium center offering a wide range of products, custom aquarium design services, and professional maintenance programs. Despite our growth, we remain committed to our founding principles of quality, expertise, and customer satisfaction.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":128,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><img src="https://aqualuxetheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/our-store.jpg" alt="AquaLuxe store interior" class="wp-image-128"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Our flagship store in Palo Alto, California</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Our Team</h2>
